Package ra.util.logging

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LogRecord.OnNotEnoughSpaceListener

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LogDelete
    Regular Delete Log file.
    LogEveryDay
    Using the Date to create a file every day, which be used to write Log. the following action: Keep the file I/O connection and will not close the file I/O connection when writing log into a file, after creating the Log file by earmark file name.
    LogRecord
    Create a file which be used to write Log. the following action: Keep the file I/O connection and will not close the file I/O connection when writing log into a file, after creating the Log file by earmark file name.
    LogSettings
    General Setting parameters for Log.
